  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThere is currently no support for the /eth/v2/debug/beacon/states API call.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nall (currently built on unstable:db8a6f81ea25ceaca1842e030f9dd1331a5ac28b)\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nRequests to this endpoint over http result in: \r\n\r\n\"BAD_REQUEST: Unsupported endpoint version: v2\"\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nA dump of the beaconstate object.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nImplement this API for eth/v2\r\n",
